Feature:  Pin movie as seen
  In order to distinguish between seen and not seen films,
  As a user,
  I want to be able to pin a movie as already seen.

  Background: There is a register user and a movie
    Given Exists a user “user1” with password “password”
    And Exists a movie 
      | name       | 
      | Marte       |

  Scenario: Pin movie as seen
    Given I login as user "user1" with password "password"
    When I pin a movie “Marte” as seen
    Then Movie “Marte” add to list seen films

  Scenario: Pin movie as seen but not logged in
    Given I'm not logged in
    When I pin a movie “Marte” as seen
    Then I'm redirected to the login form
    And Movie “Marte” doesn't add to list seen films
